# TRINITY_BIDDING_RESURRECTION_FINAL_KILLSHOT (v1.5)

Povratak u Top 20 uz pomoć hibridnog GBDT/DL ansambla i Isotonic kalibracije.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Dominacija GBDT**: 70% ansambla ostaje verno proverenim LightGBM i RF modelima, dok DL (TabNet) unosi 30% diversiteta.
> **Isotonic Shield**: Kalibracija se primenjuje samo na TabNet komponentu kako bi se sveli na minimum nelinearni driftovi pre blendinga.
> **Feature Mapping**: Medical/Clinical termini iz Trinity protokola su mapirani na Bidding domen (npr. Tanaka HR -> Volatility Index).

## Proposed Changes

### [Bidding Construction Engine]

#### [NEW] [bidding_resurrection_v1_5.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/construction_bidding/bidding_resurrection_v1_5.py)
*   **Ensemble Strategy**: 0.7 * GBDT (0.6 LGBM + 0.4 RF) + 0.3 * Isotonic(TabNet).
*   **Advanced Features**:
    *   **Clinical Anchors**: Unit-Price Bayesian Priors.
    *   **Tanaka HR**: Price Volatility Index (deviation per job).
    *   **Ischemic Burden**: High-Risk Category Load (Amount * Category Risk).
    *   **Cardiac Fatigue**: Contractor Workload (Project count history).
    *   **County-Price Index**: Location smoothing.
    *   **Contractor Win-Rate**: Bayesian Win-Rate.
*   **Validation**: 10-Fold StratifiedGroupKFold (price-binned groups).
*   **Calibration**: `sklearn.isotonic.IsotonicRegression` na OOF predikcijama DL komponente.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
*   `make test`
*   OOF Target: **< 0.435** (Auto-submit trigger).
*   Standard Deviation Check: Veto ako std > 0.05.

### 7-Gate Submit Protocol
*   Validacija svih 7 kapija pre finalnog push-a.
